tools.description:
Retrieve user information by user id.

Args:
    user_id (str): The unique identifier for the user.

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": UserInfo  # user record { "_id", "name", "role", "permission" }
    }
    or
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": str  # "User not found"
    }
